设$f\left( x \right)=\begin{cases}x, & x<1,\\\ln x, & x>1,\end{cases}g\left( x \right)=\mathrm{e}^{x - 1}$.
(1)求$\varphi\left( x \right)=f\left[ g\left( x \right) \right]$;
(2)求在$\left( -\infty,+\infty \right)$内的连续函数$y$，使之在$\left( -\infty,1 \right)$与$\left( 1,+\infty \right)$内满足微分方程$y'-y=\varphi\left( x \right)$，且$y\left( 0 \right)=0$.
